research_municipality_step.notes: Information on elected officials for Edna, TX was gathered from the City of Edna website, the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory, and the Texas State Directory. There was conflicting information regarding the Mayor Pro Tem role; the Texas State Directory lists Katrina Callis as Mayor Pro Tem, while the TML City Officials Directory lists Mike Dodds as Mayor Pro-Tem. The City of Edna website does not explicitly state who holds the Mayor Pro Tem position. For this response, Katrina Callis is listed as Mayor Pro Tem based on the Texas State Directory.
